  "title": "Luxury Watch Sales Associate | CBD | Basic + Allowance + Attractive Commission",
  "description": "<h3><strong>🔹 Job Responsibilities:</strong></h3><p>✅ Promote luxury timepieces to customers.<br />✅ Provide excellent customer service and manage relationships.<br />✅ Build and maintain a strong client network.<br />✅ Participate in corporate and customer events.<br />✅ Work as part of a dynamic team to achieve boutique sales targets, maintain store presentation, and uphold customer service excellence.</p><h3><strong>🔹 Job Requirements:</strong></h3><p>✔ GCE N/O Level or above.<br />✔ Retail sales experience preferred (luxury retail a plus!).<br />✔ Candidates with more experience may be considered for a senior role.<br />✔ Able to work retail hours, including weekends & public holidays (off days on rotation).<br />✔ Strong communication & interpersonal skills.<br />✔ Self-motivated team player with a passion for luxury watches.</p><p><br />🌟 Attractive commission structure!<br />🌟 Work in a prestigious luxury retail environment!<br />🌟 Career growth opportunities!</p><p><br /></p><p>📩 <strong>Apply Now!</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>EA Personnel Name: Nicholas Wong</strong></p><p><strong>EA Personnel No: R23113643</strong></p><p><strong>EA License No: 23C1703</strong></p>",
